 Sum in java enter value by user 
 
 Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);
         int a;
         int b;
         int sum;
         System.out.println("plz enter the first value");
         a= input.nextInt();
         System.out.println("plz enter second value ");
         b= input.nextInt();
         sum = a+b;
         System.out.println("the sum of" + a + "and" + b + " is " +sum);
       
       
       simple sum in java 
       int a=2;
         int b=4;
         int sum = a + b;
         System.out.println("the sum of " + a + " and " + b + " is " + sum );    
         
